item.title: This is maybe
item.dc:creator: @slomifier slomifier
item.description:
@slomifier wrote:

Well said (storm). I actually haven’t noticed it being a whole lot worse since my time here like 2 years ago. Few things that I have noticed that have changed:

  1. Almost like no respect for people of really high ranks (People Saying Shit About Miss Silab, Even After All Shes Done)
  2. The rules are strict as hell now. But I guess it may have been needed.
  3. There seems to be a lot more people who just cant spell, at all
  4. Seems to be a lot more java newbs (yes, newbs, not noobs) :rolleyes:

Just my opinion, take it with a grain of salt.
